'''Michaela Cottrell''' is an actress who played [[Even Piell]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']]<ref name="Star Wars: The Lightsaber Collection" /> and [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']]. She is represented by [[Warwick Davis]]'s Willow Management agency for actors under five feet tall and over seven feet tall.

